org.bytedeco.pytorch

Class InputMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.pytorch.InputMetadata
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Namespace(value="torch::autograd")
 @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=torch.class)
public class InputMetadata
extends Pointer
    Records TensorOptions, shape of the tensor, whether or not the Python dispatch key is set (tensor subclass), and, where applicable, the stream the corresponding operation took place on. If is_valid() is false, then the corresponding input is not used and may be an undefined tensor.
